        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-03-31T16:28:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I like to specify where these things come from. Give the first OS version that objc4-779.1 appeared in. (Also, periods on sentences.) So, for this one.\n\n// From 10.15.0 objc4-779.1/runtime/objc-abi.h.\n\nMake these changes to all of your references to external code throughout.",
